main event: Several objects were sighted in Wichita, Kansas, showing unusual flight patterns and a bright red glow.
interesting points: The objects were observed as being in a V formation,One object would periodically drop back and resume its position,The sighting lasted for 10-12 seconds, The objects made no noise and left no visible contrail, A separate RAF report confirmed that unidentified flying objects were investigated in Wichita around the same time.
sighted object: several unidentified lights in the sky
